# 💬 Mental Health Chat Support Bot

## 📌 Description:
A Python-based offline chatbot that gives emotional support and motivation based on the user’s mood.

## 🧠 How It Works:
- Takes mood input (happy/sad/anxious/etc.)
- Responds with helpful messages
- Works offline in Pydroid 3

